data.name: Hummus and Cucumber Toast
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and nutritious snack topped with creamy hummus and crisp cucumber slices on toasted bread.
detailedCookingInstructions: Toast the whole grain bread slices until golden brown.
Spread a generous layer of hummus on each slice of toast.
Top the hummus with cucumber slices and halved cherry tomatoes.
Drizzle with olive oil and season with salt and black pepper to taste.
Garnish with fresh dill or parsley before serving.
data.detailedName: Hummus and Cucumber Toast with Cherry Tomatoes
